txt.en: You have defeated Alagossir, the fell spirit of the storm, in Sammath Gûl.
The Sorcerer Gorothûl has met his demise at your hand in Sammath Gûl.
Sammath Gûl is a place of terror, inhabited by the sorcerer Gorothúl and the dread spirits which serve him.
You have quenched the fire of Urchír, the fell spirit of fire, in Sammath Gûl.
